<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=1692&source=Live">lucy.fnord.net/spell.html...ource=Live</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Rapture (ench59) can affect up to level 61 mobs which is enough for most tier 2 POP zones.<br>
<br>
It has a 24 second recast delay but the -1000 MR check means you can now Mez Golems and Ashenbone drakes in Hate. <br>
